      "value": "<p>When you use your Action to take the Dash action or Dodge action, you may make a single weapon attack or Unarmed Strike as part of that action.</p><p>Starting at 12th level, when you make a weapon attack or Unarmed Strike and you have no more than half of your Hit Points left you can expend one Hit Die to regain Hit Points. You can only regain Hit Points in this way once per turn.</p><p>You can regain Hit Points with this feature a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus. You regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
